Description:
Crossing the portal was a painful experience, and at some point, you lost consciousness. After a while, you finally open your eyes, though a lingering sense of dizziness remains.

A naga rushes toward you and begins to speak.

(Naga): “My name is Shn’anke, and I am part of a group fighting against the acolytes of the Great Bird. They use reptilian races as sacrifices for their twisted god. The hot-blooded races of Aquarfall have gone mad!
DescriptionAction: Please, help me free the prisoners in the temple!”
